data.description: Welcome home to this well cared for, updated ranch home. This home features three good sized main floor bedrooms. It also has one main floor full bathroom which has been updated with new LVP flooring, new toilet and a new vanity.  There are hardwood floors throughout the main floor, which have been professionally reconditioned. There is fresh paint throughout the interior, new lighting/ceiling fans, door hardware. The eat-in kitchen has been completely remodeled with brand new white shaker cabinets, flooring, and stainless steel appliances.  The lower level has a large mechanical/storage room, large laundry area. You can also find an additional brand new full bathroom in the lower level as well as a large family room! The exterior of the home has a great yard and a solid two car garage. Come check out this beautiful, move-in-ready ranch home today!  NOTE:  The lower level bathroom shower and hook up of sinks and dishwasher to take place week of 11.27.23. so it truly IS move-in ready!!!
